geetMax = O(1)
add/remove root = O(logn)

whhen adding
1. put value in the next open spot
2. push up the values //O(logn)

min heap - smallest on top

when removing 
1. swap the lower right node into the root
2. push it down

using arrays
2*i = left child
2*i+1 = right child
i/2 = parent index
counter of elements at first index

heap sort = O(nlogn) // using remove then puttijg into array
